abstract: Data2Text is a Natural Language Generation task, in which a specific domain of texts is generated faithfully based on given, structural data. The talk discusses a Proof of Concept project, in which LLMs were utilized to generate game reports for a German first division football team. It covers the necessary steps for building such a system and the problems and performances which can be expected from similar systems.
